title: Hour 3 - NBA Movement Slows Down, Kevin Millar
itunes:title: Hour 3 - NBA Movement Slows Down, Kevin Millar
description:
Dan talks about the lack of movement in the NBA with Kyrie Irving, Kevin Durant and Russell Westbrook going nowhere...for now. And he chats with former major-leaguer Kevin Millar from the All-Star Game in Los Angeles.
